{"tid":1362990,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【港鐵加價】2019年6月加價3.3%　過海每程加4毫【附新票價】","createTime":"2019-07-25T04:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T06:44:50.000Z","uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b66f5f4484898e289c6b630676729fc5ceacdeab","tid":1362990,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:45:44.000Z","msg":"社會 16:39 2019/03/28<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2310000/2310257/mtr_ticket_new_exmobile_20190328_E_V2_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2310000%2F2310257%2Fmtr_ticket_new_exmobile_20190328_E_V2_1024.png&h=5a1bf5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵加價3.3%！港鐵在可加可減機制底下，最快今年6月起可加價3.3%。不過港鐵今年需撥出2.45億元，作為車費加價後的票價97折優惠，最少維持半年，料2019年車費不會有實質上調。<br />\n<br />\n今次是港鐵過去10年以來，港鐵第9次加價。統計處今日（28日）公布去年第4季運輸業名義及實質工資指數，按年變動為5.9%，根據政府與港鐵達成的可加可減票價調整機制，港鐵今年6月可加價3.3%，加幅高於2018年的3.14%。<br />\n<br />\n以港鐵可加票價3.3%推算，部份車程的最新車費如下：<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2310000/2310257/mtr_ticket_new_inline_20190328_E_V2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2310000%2F2310257%2Fmtr_ticket_new_inline_20190328_E_V2_1024.jpg&h=41e42842&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"addb0f94c46ee77c5571ecf8fedbbd7be207b49f","tid":1362990,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"年年都加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b938ab75091498839b09ec92b452a616acb51c","tid":1362990,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f184c629ab528631ed9aa23b293bd1edf134b254","tid":1362990,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"今年加都搭，抵打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07e8a50437367ac3532a67dceb5dade250d88bc","tid":1362990,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"374441e28203fc5099c190e3938dba79a00d2061","tid":1362990,"uid":180156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:25:26.000Z","msg":"全民綠卡<br />\n綠卡在手<br />\n一卡通行"},{"pid":"603cb0473bb90e756e47ab872a94a3f036bf47a5","tid":1362990,"uid":289296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"全民免費搭港鐵最少一個月"}]}